{"arkId":"cl010099369","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099369","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Bo\u00eete \u00e0 musique de forme ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Bo\u00eete \u00e0 musique de forme ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1800 - 1815","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1800,"endYear":1815,"imprecision":"vers","text":"D\u00e9but du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"R\u00e9mond, Georges","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"avant 1746","place":"Hanau ?","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"vers 1820","place":"Gen\u00e8ve","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Rochat fr\u00e8res","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6793","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La bo\u00eete \u00e0 musique ovale est enti\u00e8rement \u00e9maill\u00e9e de bleu roi translucide sur fond guilloch\u00e9 de chevrons. Une inscription en petits brillants sur le couvercle et sur la b\u00e2te : \u0022ecoutez ma voix et admirez moi\u0022. Le couvercle ouvrant \u00e0 charni\u00e8res est \u00e9vid\u00e9 sur son milieu laissant voir un m\u00e9daillon ovale peint en \u00e9mail d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne dans le genre d\u0027Angelica Kaufmann : un adolescent prenant la main d\u0027une jeune femme drap\u00e9e assise devant une table charg\u00e9e de fruits. Ce m\u00e9daillon actionn\u00e9 par un ressort, d\u00e9couvre un oiseau chanteur en plumes qui se dresse et bat des ailes en sifflant.\r\nLe dessous de la boite ouvre \u00e0 charni\u00e8res. Sur la b\u00e2te, de part et d\u0027autre des inscriptions, quatre double pilastres cannel\u00e9s blancs et bleus opaques avec une cassolette dor\u00e9e. Bordures d\u0027encadrement en or cisel\u00e9 avec fleurons.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; \u0022Ecoutez ma voix et admirez moi\u0022 en brillant sur le couvercle et sur la b\u00e2te.\r ; FR.407.167. sur le m\u00e9canisme\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; GRC couronn\u00e9e : Georges R\u00e9mond et Cie (orf\u00e8vre) et FR : Les fr\u00e8res Rochat (horlogers)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,4","displayDimension":"3,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"9,8","displayDimension":"9,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau secondaire : diamant (petits brillants formant l\u0027inscription)\r\nMat\u00e9riau secondaire : plume\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Gen\u00e8ve (Europe-\u003ESuisse)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection baron Basile de Schlichting (1857-1914) Paris. Legs 1914","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Schlichting, Basile de","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1914","startYear":1914,"endYear":1914}]}],"owned